​Master Control Commands
Type m followed by these words to control the beast:
​m up
The Resurrection. Starts your entire media stack (Jellyfin, Sonarr, etc.) in the background.
​m status
The Vitals. Shows your drive space, GPU temp, and which apps are alive right on your phone.
​m gpu
The Pulse. A live look at your NVIDIA GTX 750's transcoding load.
​m mount
The Vault Refresh. Forces the system to re-scan for your Expansion drive if it didn't show up.
​m ps
The Roll Call. Lists every running container and the network ports they are using.
​m reset
The Nuclear Fix. Wipes the temporary cache and restarts every app from scratch.
​m gui-on
The Re-Head. Emergency command to bring back the Desktop GUI (requires reboot).
​m gui-off
The Beheading. Returns the system to pure Headless mode to save RAM (requires reboot).
